DaoxinDaireceivedtheB.Eng.degreefromtheDepartmentofOpticalEngineeringofZhejiangUniversity(ZJU,China)in2000andthenbecomeaPh.D.studentinthesamedepartment.In2004hebecameanexchangePh.D.studentintheRoyalInstituteofTechnology(KTH,Sweden)andobtainedhisPh.D.degreetherein2005.LaterhejoinedinZJUasanassistantprofessorandbecameanassociateprofessorinAug.2007.HeworkedatBowersGroupintheUniversityofCaliforniaatSantaBarbara(UCSB)asavisitingscholarduringtheyears2008~2011.DaoxinDaibecameafullprofessorinthedepartmentofOpticalEngineeringofZJUinDec.2011.
Hiscurrentresearchinterestsincludesiliconmicro-/nano-photonicsforopticalcommunications,opticalinterconnections,andopticalsensing.Hehaspublishedover120refereedinternationaljournalspapers,andhasbeeninvitedtogivemorethan20invitedtalks.Dr.Daihasseveredasprogramcommitteemembersorsessionchairsonsometopinternationalconferences,likeOFC/NFOEC2015(USA),OFC/NFOEC2014(USA),OFC/NFOEC2013(USA).HehasbeenworkingastheExecutive/AssociateEditorof&quot;IEEEPhotonicsTechnologyLetters&quot;,&ldquo;OpticalandQuantumElectronics&rdquo;and&quot;PhotonicsResearch&quot;.
